Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.88,0:00:02.52,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I've heard it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.99,0:00:07.16,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...the fact that Index really has\Ncommitted 103,000 grimoires to memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:09.98,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...which is why she is being targeted...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:15.32,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, she never said "help me" even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.35,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:18.99,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:24.85,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,500)\pos(1154,562)}#04 Perfect Memorization
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:26.05,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:34.89,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,There's... no one?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:39.74,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a rune.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:46.85,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,A rune that removed all people from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:51.89,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:54.57,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki Kaori is my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:01:00.39,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I would rather not mention my other name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.34,0:01:02.54,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Your other name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:04.62,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,My magic name, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:11.46,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're from the Magic Cabal, like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:13.44,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I will get straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:17.26,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to secure that girl before I mention my magic name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:18.89,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And if I refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:21.64,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Then I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:26.17,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just need to state my name, then secure her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:36.07,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I will repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.09,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to secure that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.09,0:01:41.91,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...before I mention my magic name...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:44.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:47.25,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I have no reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:50.14,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...to surrender to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:54.46,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I will repeat myself as many times as necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:09.39,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,The speed of the slash wreathed by my Shichiten Shichitou, Nanasen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:12.80,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,kills someone seven times over in a\Ntime period we refer to as a "split second".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:12.80,Note,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Shichiten Shichitou literally means "Seven Heaven Seven Swords",\Nand Nanasen literally means "Seven Rays"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.19,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't think it's wrong to call it "certain death".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:18.12,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:19.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even see a single slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:21.63,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.31,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,With my right hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.67,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I have received the report from Stiyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:32.54,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, your right hand can neutralize magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:36.39,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't that mean that as long as you don't touch it with your right hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.39,0:02:37.88,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,you wouldn't be able of doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:40.70,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:42.95,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Leap straight at her without any thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:48.98,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Nanasen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:02:59.68,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I will repeat myself as many times as necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:08.77,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I do not understand what is driving you to fight so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:11.34,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Nanasen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:19.45,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:26.39,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's not disappearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.02,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ultra-thin wires?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:38.27,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,She... hides all these wires while she maneuvers her katana?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:42.68,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're... not a magician?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:44.74,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I have just mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.99,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...that I heard Stiyl's story...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:50.02,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then your long katana's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:53.33,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,My Shichiten Shichitou is not an object for decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:58.69,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits you after going through Nanasen, is the truth, "Yuisen".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:58.69,Note,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Yuisen literally translates to "The Only Ray"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:03.33,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I have yet to mention my magic name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.31,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not make me mention it, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:11.27,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I do not wish to mention that name ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:16.65,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender? Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:18.45,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:20.32,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.54,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:24.36,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I said, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:26.91,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You emotionless bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:30.61,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Nanasen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:57.52,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it quite enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:05:02.01,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe you have any reason to be fighting this much for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:03.61,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:05.93,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you killing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:10.62,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanted to, you could've given me your "certain death" anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:14.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're still a person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.50,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...that has enough sense to not kill me at this stage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:20.42,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should know why, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:23.57,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing a little girl through the crowds...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:26.09,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Slashing her back with your katana...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:29.72,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That shouldn't be tolerated...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.54,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:36.47,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,She's lost her memories because of you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:41.21,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,How badly did you chase her to make her lose even her memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:46.23,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the kind of loser that has to fight in a desperate fashion...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:51.62,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...and yet not able to even protect one single girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:58.69,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I am just a weak being that can only chew on\Nmy fingers as I watch you guys take her away...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:01.87,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...but you're different, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:06.29,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,With the power you have, you can protect whoever and whatever you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.48,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...you can save whoever and whatever you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:11.00,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...yet, why is this the only action you're taking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:15.56,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:23.30,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not... doing this because I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:27.53,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the organization I belong to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:29.45,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...is Necessarius...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:34.83,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's... the same one Index belongs to,\Nthe English Purist Church!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.01,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,She is my colleague...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:40.36,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...and a very important friend of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:45.15,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't intend to slash her back either!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:52.14,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't... know the Walking Church had been destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:57.71,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I only slashed her knowing she wouldn't be injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:06:58.86,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:00.73,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.52,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you even slash your friend from behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:07.32,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't secure her in that manner, she won't be able to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.03,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Her "perfect memorization" ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:12.16,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect... memorization?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:15.16,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,That is the reason behind all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:27.23,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,By perfect memorization...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.03,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...are you referring to the 103,000 grimoires?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:36.86,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,She said they were all inputted into her brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:40.58,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,The human brain's capacity is rather minimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:44.25,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,But, by forgetting unnecessary memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:46.70,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,one is unconsciously organizing their own brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:48.89,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,That's why humans are able to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:50.21,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.68,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...she can't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:58.06,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,From the number of leaves on street-side trees...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:00.87,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...to the faces of everyone moving\Nin and out during rush hour periods...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:04.52,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...even the shape of every single drop of rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:10.19,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Her brain fills up immediately with such unnecessary information.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.55,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, just wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:16.58,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys all belong to the same organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:19.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,then why is Index calling you evil magicians?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:21.65,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Or, are you telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:24.26,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...that Index is lying to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:27.24,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,She has not lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:34.38,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that we are all members of Necessarius... nor the real reason why she's being chased...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:38.23,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...she doesn't remember any of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:43.23,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,That is why she is forced to make her own judgment...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:51.51,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,That it is logical to think the magicians after\Nthe 103,000 grimoires are from the Magic Cabal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:57.36,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But Index has perfect memorization, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:02.76,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why did she lose her memory from this past year in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.35,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,She did not lose her memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.77,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We erased it, to be exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.01,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Erased?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.18,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.82,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,With magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.21,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:19.59,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You were Index's friend, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:24.26,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Index an important friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.75,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:29.06,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Because we had no choice but to erase her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:37.38,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Because if we didn't... she would have died...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:52.86,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,85% of her brain is allocated to the 103,000 grimoires.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:57.81,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,That is why she can only use 15% of a normal person's brain capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:03.73,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,If information keeps flooding into the remaining 15%, her brain will...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:05.52,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Other than erasing her memory, there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:09.91,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...No other way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:11.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:16.20,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Memory erasure takes place in exact one year periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:20.45,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Memory erasure wouldn't be possible if it didn't occur at that exact moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:23.99,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Only three more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:25.99,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Three days...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.80,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We have no intention of harming her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:34.73,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, no one else is able to save her other than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:37.14,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Could you hand her over to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:39.45,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Before I mention my magic name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:47.89,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,And, by erasing her memory, she won't remember anything about you, no matter how much you think of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:55.69,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Saving her brings you no benefit at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:00.36,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:05.45,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Like this has anything to do with whether she remembers me or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:09.46,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get it, then let me tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:12.43,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm Index's friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:17.95,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been her friend, and I always will be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:21.71,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it wasn't written in The Bible, at least this is true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:24.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I knew something was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:26.85,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If it's as simple as her forgetting things,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:29.54,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,all you need to do is explain everything and clear the misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:31.98,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you leave it as a misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:34.48,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you chase after her as an enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:37.19,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you just give up on her like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:39.15,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What about her own feeling-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:41.36,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth, you amateur!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:44.41,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk as if you knew what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:50.24,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think we went through\Nall this time by taking away her memories?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.72,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently you see Stiyl as an enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:58.86,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,but do you even know how he felt as he watched you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:02.80,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know how much resolve he had when he presented himself as an enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:08.13,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl's feelings as he dishonors himself for the sake of saving his important friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:11.22,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...would someone like you have any clue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:19.19,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We did what we could, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:21.05,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We did, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:24.22,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We spent all spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.70,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,All summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:26.95,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,All fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:27.76,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,All winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:30.78,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We created memories, and so that she didn't forget them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:33.12,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,we made a single promise with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:36.10,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,and we gave her a diary and album for her to carry inside her heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:39.57,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.12,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...it didn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:44.33,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we went back and made more memories with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:46.53,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how many times we repeated that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:50.24,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...memories of her family, friends, lovers...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.71,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,...they were all reset to zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.41,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't handle it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:13:01.36,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't bear to see her smile anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:03.86,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:10.28,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's just your own bullshit logic...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:16.70,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't think for Index's sake a single moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:21.99,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame your own gutlessness on Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:27.11,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so scared of seeing her lose one year's worth of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:31.56,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If you just give her more blessed memories the next year...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:36.64,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If she knows there's happiness waiting for her the year after to let her conquer the fear of losing this year's memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:42.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...then no one needs to run away anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:45.57,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that all there is to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:50.34,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Are you protecting people just because you have power?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:52.12,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:53.49,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how it is, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:57.16,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You acquired power {\i1}because{\fscx50} {\r} you have something you want to protect, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.78,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you acquire power?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:03.31,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you want to protect with those hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:06.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then what the hell are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.76,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,With that much power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:11.21,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,with such a versatile power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:15.47,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,why are you... so... incompetent...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:32.53,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,All done?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:49.80,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Oneesama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:51.26,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be in such a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:53.17,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroko, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:56.74,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,While you keep saying curfew, curfew,\Nyou've been dragging me to place after place...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:58.28,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be held responsible if we're back late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:14:59.56,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Oneesama~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.61,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.32,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:08.86,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,A razor sharp cut like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:12.14,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, a prank by someone with robotic control powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.30,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,A prank, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:18.20,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,A task for Judgment, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:20.21,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Kuroko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.98,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do with all this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:36.60,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Oneesama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.21,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.00,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:58.41,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.24,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:03.06,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, you shouldn't get up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:08.31,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The sun's in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:10.82,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...which means a night has gone by...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:12.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:14.41,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Not one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:16.49,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:18.03,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Three days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:21.02,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,How could I have slept for that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:22.91,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Three days...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:27.61,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Memory erasure takes place in exact one year periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.98,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Only three more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:31.84,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.27,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:34.00,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:40.95,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that Index still remembers me means the memory erasure hasn't taken place yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:44.91,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And neither does Index seem any different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:47.85,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:49.90,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:54.38,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:59.17,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Komoe said that you were lying unconscious in the middle of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:04.79,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Komoe was also the one that carried\Nyour beaten body back to the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:07.86,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:13.66,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think at all that you were fighting against other magicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:15.76,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:20.33,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I... couldn't save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:28.79,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this ridiculous bandage wrapping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.86,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,A bit much, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:35.37,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that was necessary to heal wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.14,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as reliable as magic, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:39.65,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:42.89,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine even if you don't use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:44.74,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:49.59,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, you still don't believe in magic even after all this, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:52.16,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,You're as stubborn as a person with a one-sided love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:54.12,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:18:00.95,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If at all possible, I don't want to see the look on your face when you speak about magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:02.60,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:05.06,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:06.58,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Woke up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:12.59,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,But, I don't think I want to hear about how I am when I wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:18.39,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The voice I have when I'm unconscious is like talking in dreams... it's very embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:20.68,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:25.47,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,...it feels like I'm gradually becoming a cold machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:27.27,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,...and it scares me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:30.04,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:34.58,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:38.59,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Want to eat something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.83,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Index... -san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:47.39,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:49.08,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,so I know how to take care of a sick person, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:55.05,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... please allow me the time to think over this deeply, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:56.39,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:57.76,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Not hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:02.63,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:18.69,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:21.16,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Komoe, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:23.99,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in front of my home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:26.85,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijyo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:30.45,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what's going on, but we have some guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:37.48,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:38.13,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing here now-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:39.66,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:44.17,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even run away easily with that body of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:47.40,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:51.50,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Index has been running away from these people on her own...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:56.40,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...but if she has to carry the burden of an injured person in me, then it's a different story...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:20:00.87,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In order to more efficiently and safely secure Index,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:02.37,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,they want to use me as...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:03.49,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.23,0:20:07.37,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, I'll go anywhere with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:10.29,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:11.75,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:14.93,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I beg you, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:19.00,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't hurt Touma anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:28.31,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:26.73,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, at midnight,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:29.52,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,the ritual to erase Index's memories will take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:32.07,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:33.92,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I will get you out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:35.78,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Limit".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:37.87,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:39.32,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,this epic will begin!
